---
title: Chicken, Bacon & Veggie Fried Rice with Roasted Cashews
description: Fried rice is one of our year-round favourites, and this is one of our best flavour combinations ever. Not only does it taste great, but it’s a real feast of textures, too – from succulent chicken to crunchy roasted cashews.
